---
title: Crispy Orloni-Style Tilapia Tacos with Chipotle Mayo, Zesty Slaw, Pickled Jalapeño & Radishes
description: Nothing brings your family (or chosen family!) together quite like taco night. And these tacos—inspired by one of Mantis' favorite alien snacks—deliver all the feels. Crispy battered tilapia is piled into warm tortillas and topped with a crunchy cabbage slaw and a drizzle of creamy chipotle mayo. But wait! We’re also delivering a double explosion of flavor to your tacos with pickled jalapeño rounds and radishes for a spicy punch. All of these delicious elements join forces for an out-of-this-world eating experience.
